<p>I have an html page deployed in one tomcat. When I click a link on the page, it takes me to a page deployed in another tomcat. </p>  <p>Now, I have to use struts to do this,</p>  <pre><code>&lt;action name="forward" class="xyz"&gt;         &lt;result&gt;abc.jsp&lt;/result&gt; &lt;/action&gt; </code></pre>  <p>But if I use it like this, the new html file opens in same tomcat.</p>